&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Behavox Platform Functionality (Power User, Admin, Data Admin Personas)&lt;/strong&gt; – In-depth understanding of workflows, permissions, alert management, data quality, and reporting capabilities required to configure and support key client personas. Applies this knowledge to deliver accurate configurations and structured enablement&lt;/li&gt;
